    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Oath of Vengeance is a solemn commitment to punish those who have committed a grievous sin. When evil forces slaughter helpless villagers, when an entire people turns against the will of the gods, when a thieves' guild grows too violent and powerful, when a dragon rampages through the countryside – at times like these, paladins arise and swear an Oath of Vengeance to set right that which has gone wrong. To these paladins – sometimes called avengers or dark knights – their own purity is not as important as delivering justice.</p><h3>Oath of Glory Spells</h3><table><thead><tr><td><strong>Paladin Level</strong></td><td><strong>Spells</strong></td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3rd</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.Hj5boJxDzzVxwtNw]{Bane}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.7UkxyEz38pGsAP6v]{Hunter's Mark}</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.NXOXaNWD6HazQkmY]{Hold Person}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.8yienSU9GWw8t1us]{Misty Step}</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.Ph1qFaV8cGDh0KRY]{Haste}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.mosnEaBOzuz4bT8y]{Protection from Energy}</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.NtdmlSBrs1mCCgQi]{Banishment}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.m9ecvbgxX3lliiA9]{Dimension Door}</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.R6HwuSHAkPV4kAzF]{Hold Monster}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.yacJyg7wuVIGvoWk]{Scrying}</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Oath of Vengeance Features</h3><p>3rd: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.UDvUNV1USjYlvXou]{Tenets of Vengeance}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.saKAmKZxJD0N4mly]{Abjure Enemy}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.OsW6GLQmQ4FpU9W0]{Vow of Emnity}</p><p>7th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.ImoHoFh0leHXn43T]{Relentless Avenger}</p><p>15th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.WhJLx1Brz55nOO4L]{Soul of Vengeance}</p><p>20th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.rOqM1VDWMJr85Fvx]{Avenging Angel}</p>",
